Here’s a structured roadmap and investor pitch deck outline for your AI-powered Virtual Sales & Support Representative.

---

## **🚀 AI Sales & Support Assistant – Prototype Roadmap**

### **Phase 1: Research & Planning (Month 1)**
- Define core AI capabilities: sales, customer service, support  
- Identify target industries (e.g., SaaS, e-commerce, fintech, telecom)  
- Select tech stack & cloud providers (AWS, GCP, Azure)  
- Research competitor solutions (Drift, Ada, Dialpad AI, etc.)  
- Develop initial AI conversation models (GPT-4, Gemini, Llama)  

### **Phase 2: MVP Development (Months 2-4)**
✅ **Core AI Conversational Agent**  
   - Train AI for sales & support conversations  
   - Implement speech-to-text & text-to-speech  
   - Build chatbot for website, WhatsApp, and email  

✅ **CRM & Ticketing System Integration**  
   - Connect to Salesforce, HubSpot, Zendesk APIs  
   - Enable AI-powered lead tracking & ticket creation  

✅ **AI Call Automation (Twilio, Vonage, Google Dialogflow)**  
   - AI makes and receives calls  
   - Conducts sales pitches, schedules meetings, follows up  

✅ **Basic Dashboard for Analytics & Monitoring**  
   - View AI-generated leads, sales calls, and support tickets  

### **Phase 3: Beta Testing & Refinement (Months 5-6)**
- Run pilot tests with real businesses  
- Improve AI conversations based on feedback  
- Optimize sales conversion and customer resolution rates  

### **Phase 4: Full-Scale Deployment & Growth (Months 7+)**
- Launch product with paid subscription model  
- Scale AI interactions with automation & predictive analytics  
- Expand integrations with enterprise tools  
- Secure funding or partnerships for scaling  

---

## **📊 AI Sales & Support Assistant – Investor Pitch Deck**  

### **1️⃣ Introduction**  
- **Problem Statement**: Businesses lose revenue due to slow sales & poor customer service.  
- **Solution**: AI-powered assistant that automates sales, follow-ups, and support calls.  

### **2️⃣ Market Opportunity**  
- Global AI customer service market = **$11B+ (2024), growing at 23% CAGR**  
- Sales automation AI expected to **disrupt $2T in global sales**  

### **3️⃣ Product Overview**  
- AI interacts like a human: Voice, Chat, Email, WhatsApp  
- Automates **lead generation, follow-ups, and support tickets**  
- Integrates with CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot) & ticketing (Zendesk, Freshdesk)  

### **4️⃣ Technology Stack**  
- **AI & NLP**: GPT-4, Gemini, Whisper (speech-to-text), Polly (text-to-speech)  
- **Cloud**: AWS, GCP, Azure  
- **CRM & Support**: Salesforce, Zendesk API integration  
- **Voice Calls**: Twilio, Vonage AI-powered dialer  

### **5️⃣ Business Model**  
💰 **Subscription-based SaaS pricing**:  
   - **Basic**: $49/month (chat-only AI)  
   - **Pro**: $199/month (calls + CRM integrations)  
   - **Enterprise**: Custom pricing  

🔁 **Additional Revenue Streams**:  
   - API access for businesses  
   - White-label AI for enterprises  
   - AI training for specific industries  

### **6️⃣ Competitive Advantage**  
- 🏆 **Smarter than chatbots** – AI understands & adapts  
- 📞 **Handles voice calls & chats** – Not just a text bot  
- 🚀 **End-to-end automation** – From lead gen to closing deals  

### **7️⃣ Financial Projections**  
- Year 1: **$500K ARR** (1,000 businesses @ $49-$199/mo)  
- Year 3: **$5M ARR** (10K businesses, scaling to enterprise deals)  

### **8️⃣ Go-To-Market Strategy**  
- Target SMEs, e-commerce, fintech, and SaaS startups  
- Use **LinkedIn outreach, SEO, and partnerships** for traction  
- Offer **freemium trial model** to convert users  

### **9️⃣ Funding Ask**  
🔹 **Seeking $500K seed funding** to scale AI development & marketing  
🔹 **Use of Funds**:  
   - 50% R&D (AI refinement, integrations)  
   - 30% Sales & Marketing  
   - 20% Cloud & Infrastructure  

### **🔟 Conclusion & Call to Action**  
🚀 Join us in revolutionizing sales & support with AI!  
